headline: Jack Henry Releases 2025 Sustainability Report
summary: Jack Henry™ (NASDAQ: JKHY) today announced the publication of its 2025 Sustainability Report, highlighting the company's ongoing commitment to delivering lasting value for associates, clients, communities, stockholders, and the environment through responsible business practices.
